{"data":{"doc":{"editUrl":"https://github.com/JoinColony/colonyNetwork/edit/develop/docs/_Docs_Extensions.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Extensions"},"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{"className":["md-toc"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#onetxpayment"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OneTxPayment"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#oldroles"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OldRoles"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"glider"}]},{"type":"text","value":" provides the option of \"extensions\" to the basic functionality of a colony through the use of "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"extensions"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Extensions are other smart contracts that have been given permissions to interact with a colony in a specified domain. Extensions can be used for many purposes, such as bundling transactions, automating certain actions, or something else entirely."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Extensions do not need to be part of the colonyNetwork codebase to function, the contract address simply must be given permission to call the desired functions as a member of the colony."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Currently there are two extensions 'officially' supported, but more may be added in the future. These extensions are written with dapp support in mind, and emit events to inform a user interface whether a colony has an extension enabled or not."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Supported extensions implement a 'factory' design pattern to make deployment straightforward for users, but custom extensions need not follow this pattern. "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"onetxpayment"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#onetxpayment","ariaLabel":"onetxpayment permalink","className":["md-heading-link"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"OneTxPayment"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ordinarily payments require more than one transaction, because the payment lifecycle requires more than one permissioned "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/colonynetwork/docs-modular-permissions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"role"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In some use cases, there might be a need for one authorized individual to be able to create, funds, and finalize a payment within a single transaction."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OneTxPayment"}]},{"type":"text","value":" extension adds this functionality by adding a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"makePayment"}]},{"type":"text","value":" function which requires the caller to have "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"both"}]},{"type":"text","value":" funding and administration ability within the domain of the payment."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"oldroles"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#oldroles","ariaLabel":"oldroles permalink","className":["md-heading-link"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"OldRoles"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In earlier versions of the colonyNetwork, only two roles existed for permissioned accounts: \"Founder\", and \"Admin\""}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OldRoles"}]},{"type":"text","value":" extension bundles the roles in the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"glider"}]},{"type":"text","value":" release together into super-roles that have the same abilities as the original \"Founder\" (root) and \"Admin\" (funding, administration, architecture) roles."}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}}},"project":{"slug":"colonynetwork","name":"colonyNetwork","logo":"img/colonyNetwork_color.svg","logoSmall":"img/logomark_colonyNetwork_blue.svg","repoUrl":"https://github.com/JoinColony/colonyNetwork","sectionOrder":["intro","docs","bug-bounty-program","whitepaper-tldr","api"],"sectionTranslations":null,"sections":[{"name":"Docs","slug":"docs","docs":[{"slug":"extensions","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-extensions"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Extensions","order":5,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"get-started","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-get-started"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Get Started","order":7,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"overview","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-overview"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Overview","order":1,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"modular-permissions","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-modular-permissions"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Modular Permissions","order":4,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"releases","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-releases"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Releases","order":3,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"reputation-mining-client","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-reputation-mining-client"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Reputation Mining Client","order":6,"section":"Docs"}},{"slug":"the-delegate-proxy-pattern","fields":{"locale":"en","slug":"/colonynetwork/docs-the-delegate-proxy-pattern